# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [0.2.0] — 2026-04-15

### Changed — Architecture migration: VITS → F5-TTS

Complete replacement of the VITS GAN-based architecture with F5-TTS (OT-Conditional Flow Matching + Diffusion Transformer).

#### Removed

- VITS model stack: posterior encoder, stochastic duration predictor, HiFi-GAN vocoder, multi-period/multi-scale discriminators
- Adversarial losses: `generator_loss`, `discriminator_loss`, `feature_loss`, `kl_loss`, `duration_loss`
- `MongolianPhonemizer` (stub alias, replaced by `CyrillicTokenizer`)
- Stub files: `discriminator.py`, `duration_predictor.py`, `posterior.py`, `vits.py`, `phonemizer.py`
- `VITSTrainer` and all VITS-specific training infrastructure

#### Added

- `CyrillicTokenizer` — character-level tokenizer for Mongolian + Kazakh Cyrillic, vocab size 67
  - Language tags: `[LANG_MN]`, `[LANG_KZ]`
  - Attribute tags: `[FEMALE]`, `[MALE]`, `[YOUNG]`, `[MIDDLE]`, `[ELDERLY]`
- `TextConvEmbed` — character embedding + depthwise conv stack encoder (`src/models/encoder.py`)
- `DiT` — Diffusion Transformer backbone with RoPE, AdaLN, SwiGLU FFN (`src/models/dit.py`, `modules.py`)
- `CFM` — OT-Conditional Flow Matching: training forward + Euler ODE inference (`src/models/flow.py`)
- `VocosDecoder` — ConvNeXt + iSTFT vocoder, no GAN (`src/models/decoder.py`)
- `F5TTS` — top-level model with voice-cloning (Option A) and attribute-token (Option B) inference (`src/models/f5tts.py`)
- `cfm_loss` — single MSE loss on the velocity field (`src/training/losses.py`)
- `F5Trainer` — AdamW + LinearLR warmup + EMA training loop (`src/training/trainer.py`)
- `CheckpointManager.load_pretrained_f5tts()` — key-remapping loader for official `.safetensors` checkpoints

#### Changed

- Audio defaults: **24 000 Hz** sample rate, **100 mel bins**, n_fft 1024, hop 256 (was 22 050 Hz / 80 mel)
- `TextCleaner` now wraps `CyrillicTokenizer`; added Kazakh-specific characters to `ALLOWED_CHARS`
- `CheckpointManager` updated for single optimizer + EMA (removed dual optimizer_g/optimizer_d)
- All sample-rate defaults updated to 24 000 in `denoiser.py`, `hf_wrapper.py`, `clean_local_cv.py`, `prepare.py`
- Configs renamed to reflect F5-TTS Small (local) and Base (RunPod) sizes
- `scripts/train.py` — added `--pretrain-ckpt`, `--lang`, `--lang-column` flags
- `scripts/infer.py` — rewritten for voice cloning (`--ref-audio`) and attribute tokens (`--attr-tokens`)

## [0.1.0] — 2026-01-28

- Initial VITS architecture implementation for Mongolian TTS
- Multi-speaker support (male / female speaker IDs)
- DeepFilterNet audio denoising (`AudioDenoiser`)
- Mongolian text normalization — `NumberNormalizer` (cardinal + ordinal)
- Hugging Face dataset and model hub integration
- RunPod cloud training configuration and setup script
- Structured logging for container environments (tqdm disable mode)
- Multi-GPU distributed training with `DistributedDataParallel`
- TensorBoard integration
- Checkpoint management with automatic cleanup and HF Hub push
